  "content": "<h1>Making a Character</h1>\n<p class=\"p1\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Helvetica;\">First get familiar with the layout of the character sheet.</p>\n<p class=\"p1\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Helvetica;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"p1\" style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Helvetica;\">@JournalEntry[SNaZuDLPs3AolJKN]{Character Sheet}</li>\n<li class=\"p1\" style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Helvetica;\">@JournalEntry[jlFjtjCciMBZvCfh]{Tab: Combat}</li>\n<li class=\"p1\" style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Helvetica;\">@JournalEntry[MzYKFxArNqAu42sW]{Tab: Talents}</li>\n<li class=\"p1\" style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Helvetica;\">Tab: Magic</li>\n<li class=\"p1\" style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Helvetica;\">Tab: Inventory</li>\n<li class=\"p1\" style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Helvetica;\">Tab: Background</li>\n<li class=\"p1\" style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Helvetica;\">Actor Mods</li>\n</ul>\n<p class=\"p1\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Helvetica;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p class=\"p1\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Helvetica;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<h2>Prerequisites</h2>\n<p>Buy the Core Rules book. You can't play the game without the rules.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>To get the character sheet working, you'll need to create a few things first:</p>\n<ol>\n<li>Ancestries</li>\n<li>Paths</li>\n<li>Talents</li>\n<li>Spells (if you need any)</li>\n</ol>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<h3><strong>Ancestries</strong></h3>\n<p class=\"p1\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Helvetica;\">There are 6 ancestries in the Core Rules. I'll recommend just creating them all from the beginning.</p>\n<p>@JournalEntry[kvoHFTm3wINamWr8]{Ancestries}</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<h3><strong>Paths</strong></h3>\n<p class=\"p1\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Helvetica;\">There are 4 Novice Paths, 16 Expert Paths and 64 Master Paths in the Core Rules.</p>\n<p class=\"p1\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Helvetica;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p class=\"p1\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Helvetica;\">Only create the Paths and their Talents you need. There&rsquo;s a staggering amount of content in the book and most of them you&rsquo;ll never use anyway. Slowly expand with what you need over time.</p>\n<p class=\"p1\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Helvetica;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p class=\"p1\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Helvetica;\">@JournalEntry[N8H9cpsxVdVJsG7g]{Paths}</p>\n<p class=\"p1\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Helvetica;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p class=\"p1\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Helvetica;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<h3 class=\"p1\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Helvetica;\"><strong>Spells</strong></h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: Helvetica;\">There are 30 Traditions of magic in the Core Rules.&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p class=\"p1\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Helvetica;\">I'll recommend the same approach as with Paths, only create those you need.</p>\n<p class=\"p1\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Helvetica;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p class=\"p1\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Helvetica;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<h2>Fill out your character sheet</h2>\n<ol>\n<li class=\"li1\" style=\"margin: 0px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Helvetica;\">Level: Set the starting level for your character.<br /><br /></li>\n<li class=\"li1\" style=\"margin: 0px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Helvetica;\">Ancestry: Choose an Ancestry from the list the GM has made and drag/drop it onto your character sheet.<br /><br />Edit you Ancestry and adjust your Starting Attributes according to the rules.<br /><br /></li>\n<li class=\"li1\" style=\"margin: 0px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Helvetica;\">Paths: If you start at level 1 or higher. Drag/drop a Path onto your character sheet. <br />Edit you paths and choose your attribute increases. Attributes, Characteristics, Talents and Spells will automatically be transferred to your character sheet. Some paths like the Rogue has to make some chooses on certain levels. Those chooses of Talents you have to transfer yourself.<br /><br /></li>\n<li class=\"li1\" style=\"margin: 0px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Helvetica;\">Professions: Create them on the character sheet<br /><br /></li>\n<li class=\"li1\" style=\"margin: 0px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Helvetica;\">Features: Are optional. I use them to write down Changeling Quirks, Clockwork Form, Appearance and Personality.<br /><br /></li>\n<li class=\"li1\" style=\"margin: 0px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Helvetica;\">Inventory: Enter your wealth and add your starting items.<br /><br /></li>\n<li class=\"li1\" style=\"margin: 0px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Helvetica;\"><span style=\"font-family: Helvetica;\">Religion: Write the name of your religion/belief&nbsp;and optional choose an image.</span><br /><br /></li>\n<li class=\"li1\" style=\"margin: 0px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Helvetica;\">Languages: Check them to see if they are correct.<br /><br /></li>\n<li class=\"li1\" style=\"margin: 0px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Helvetica;\">Image: Select an image for your character.<br /><br /></li>\n<li class=\"li1\" style=\"margin: 0px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Helvetica;\">Weapons: Drag/drop Weapons, Armor, Shield and Ammunition from the compendiums onto the character sheet.<br /><br /></li>\n<li class=\"li1\" style=\"margin: 0px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Helvetica;\">Background: Write something cool.</li>\n</ol>",
